y are. Have enough dignity to treat people with respect and decency in any type of communication you may be involved in. Be aware and acknowledge that there are tasks that only a few such as Lagdalen and Flarren have volunteered to do without purely selfish reasons. <br><br>Pippi Langstrump  <p><HR><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size=2>     What concerns everyone can only be resolved by everyone.                                                                   -Friedrich Dürrenmatt</font></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uplangstrump.showPublicProfile?language=EN>P Langstrump</A> at: 5/9/01 11:28:55 am<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.showPrevMessage?topicID=52.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.showNextMessage?topicID=52.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=52.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.emailToFriend?topicID=52.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.threadControl?topicID=52.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=52.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a hre